         <div type="translation">
            <ab>"The Holy Gospel according to Matthew. The book of the generation of Jesus the Christ, the son of David.;The Gospel according to Mark. The beginning of the Gospel of Jesus the Christ.;The Gospel according to Luke. Since many have have undertaken to write the words.;The Gospel according to John. In the beginning was the Word, and the Word was in the presence of God.;(Magic signs)."</ab>
